<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak " data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<h2 id="right-result">Right result</h2>

<ul>
  <li>We will provide regulatory inspection services, scientific, veterinary and technical expertise, and quality laboratory services</li>
  <li>We will provide you with information relevant to your business/your needs</li>
  <li>We will investigate the cause of any problems and do everything possible to put things right if they go wrong</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="right-treatment">Right treatment</h2>

<ul>
  <li>We will treat you in a polite and professional manner</li>
  <li>We will listen to, seek and act on feedback</li>
  <li>We will conform and comply with the <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/regulators-code">Regulators’ Code</a>
</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="on-time">On time</h2>

<ul>
  <li>We will respond immediately to reports of suspected exotic notifiable disease which pose an immediate threat to human or animal health</li>
  <li>Where appointments are agreed with you we will aim to be on time</li>
  <li>We will acknowledge correspondence and respond to complaints within 15 working days</li>
  <li>We will aim to meet our published timescales and standards</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="accessible">Accessible</h2>

<ul>
  <li>We will make sure you can contact us in ways that are simple and straightforward</li>
  <li>We will provide a 24 hour reporting service for animal health and welfare emergencies</li>
  <li>We will provide access to the right people to deal with your enquiry</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="customers">Customers</h2>

<p>In addition, we would expect customers to:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Treat staff with courtesy</li>
  <li>Keep us up to date with relevant changes to your information</li>
  <li>Keep any appointment you have with us, or let us know as soon as possible if you can’t keep it</li>
</ul>

</div>
